{"tid":1799251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Boxing Day贈興】群警突闖多區商場 店舖紛落閘：怕X咗佢哋！客人驚被追打即走","createTime":"2019-12-26T21:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T01:27:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8e2fc620686875fa6baf36027c667f4f68da52","tid":1799251,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:13:49.000Z","msg":"今個聖誕節因警員濫暴、催淚彈放題，多個商場浴血。今日Boxing Day，繼續有網民在各區發起「聖誕和你SUCK」、「SUCK the Christmas和你Shop」活動，號召港人下午到尖沙嘴海港城、銅鑼灣SOGO、旺角MOKO及大埔超級城叫口號和唱歌。結果群警突然闖進多個商場，嚇得商舖紛紛落閘、客人受驚。其中港威商場3樓一間護膚品店一度落閘，職員S小姐（化名）指，大批警員突然衝入商場，連該店客人也受驚，「怕X咗佢哋啦！有客人原本喺度都即刻走，驚會追住佢嚟打。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191226/large/1577354599_dc2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191226%2Flarge%2F1577354599_dc2c.jpg&h=ce36c63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191226/60418204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F60418204&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=97dd9c84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F60418204&h=f9d3f514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191226/60418204</a>"},{"pid":"204c29e26e2ff11007ca4b80ea58b498bc4b3e41","tid":1799251,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"好多客戶都表態係班狗阻撚住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060fe0955d5b5f2aff3e88fd0b82728ca1c8e4b7","tid":1799251,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:17:38.000Z","msg":"怕x左佢<br />\n<br />\nx stands for &hellip;"},{"pid":"9e19f77c36ccc4d769243003c8405837881346dc","tid":1799251,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2